  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in an epic adventure! You were once a powerful baron, but a dark mage accused you of treason and banished you into exile. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now it’s time to change your fate! Fight your way back, defeat the sinister mage, and save the king.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you reclaim the honor and power that are rightfully yours? Your journey begins now! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984260/extras/f938c52a756e7916551e4c2762c712eb.apng?t=1743355951\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984260/extras/f938c52a756e7916551e4c2762c712eb.poster.avif?t=1743355951\" class=\"bb_img\" width=180 height=180 /></picture></span>                               <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984260/extras/8233a24989c01af12a1688c8ea410e8a.poster.avif?t=1743355951\" width=180 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984260/extras/8233a24989c01af12a1688c8ea410e8a.webm?t=1743355951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>COMBAT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your main weapon, a big axe, to defeat enemies. Collect exploding potions and use them agains your opponents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984260/extras/570dde7fb748849650362b7e060099e2.poster.avif?t=1743355951\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984260/extras/570dde7fb748849650362b7e060099e2.webm?t=1743355951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984260/extras/570dde7fb748849650362b7e060099e2.mp4?t=1743355951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPLORE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A vast world full of discoveries awaits you! Explore 24 different  levels across five unique worlds, each presenting exciting challenges. From endless desert landscapes and dense forests to majestic mountains and mysterious castles – experience breathtaking locations and embrace every adventure.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984260/extras/495417a35b4ebea9d7059cd62a9e27f8.avif?t=1743355951\" width=600 height=192 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BOSSFIGHTS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use all your skills to defeat powerful bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984260/extras/3ebdb05ade25dd848edc587fe88232da.apng?t=1743355951\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984260/extras/3ebdb05ade25dd848edc587fe88232da.poster.avif?t=1743355951\" class=\"bb_img\" width=180 height=180 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MEET HELPERS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet friendly characters, which you can play and use new weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984260/extras/acf0ca4835cb5a7916a101fa4c1fe6d6.apng?t=1743355951\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984260/extras/acf0ca4835cb5a7916a101fa4c1fe6d6.poster.avif?t=1743355951\" class=\"bb_img\" width=180 height=100 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984260/extras/0ba6f9a9c5dc0dcd2dffc45bf2ff68e7.apng?t=1743355951\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984260/extras/0ba6f9a9c5dc0dcd2dffc45bf2ff68e7.poster.avif?t=1743355951\" class=\"bb_img\" width=180 height=100 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PLAY WITH A FRIEND</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In co-op multiplayer mode, you can enjoy your adventure with a friend.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MORE AWAITS YOU</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect coins to purchase powerful items from merchants. Hidden diamonds and various achievements will keep you engaged even after you've completed the game.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in an epic adventure! You were once a powerful baron, but a dark mage accused you of treason and banished you into exile. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now it’s time to change your fate! Fight your way back, defeat the sinister mage, and save the king.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you reclaim the honor and power that are rightfully yours? Your journey begins now! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984260/extras/f938c52a756e7916551e4c2762c712eb.apng?t=1743355951\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984260/extras/f938c52a756e7916551e4c2762c712eb.poster.avif?t=1743355951\" class=\"bb_img\" width=180 height=180 /></picture></span>                               <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984260/extras/8233a24989c01af12a1688c8ea410e8a.poster.avif?t=1743355951\" width=180 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984260/extras/8233a24989c01af12a1688c8ea410e8a.webm?t=1743355951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>COMBAT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your main weapon, a big axe, to defeat enemies. Collect exploding potions and use them agains your opponents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984260/extras/570dde7fb748849650362b7e060099e2.poster.avif?t=1743355951\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984260/extras/570dde7fb748849650362b7e060099e2.webm?t=1743355951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984260/extras/570dde7fb748849650362b7e060099e2.mp4?t=1743355951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPLORE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A vast world full of discoveries awaits you! Explore 24 different  levels across five unique worlds, each presenting exciting challenges. From endless desert landscapes and dense forests to majestic mountains and mysterious castles – experience breathtaking locations and embrace every adventure.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984260/extras/495417a35b4ebea9d7059cd62a9e27f8.avif?t=1743355951\" width=600 height=192 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BOSSFIGHTS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use all your skills to defeat powerful bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984260/extras/3ebdb05ade25dd848edc587fe88232da.apng?t=1743355951\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984260/extras/3ebdb05ade25dd848edc587fe88232da.poster.avif?t=1743355951\" class=\"bb_img\" width=180 height=180 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MEET HELPERS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet friendly characters, which you can play and use new weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984260/extras/acf0ca4835cb5a7916a101fa4c1fe6d6.apng?t=1743355951\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984260/extras/acf0ca4835cb5a7916a101fa4c1fe6d6.poster.avif?t=1743355951\" class=\"bb_img\" width=180 height=100 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984260/extras/0ba6f9a9c5dc0dcd2dffc45bf2ff68e7.apng?t=1743355951\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984260/extras/0ba6f9a9c5dc0dcd2dffc45bf2ff68e7.poster.avif?t=1743355951\" class=\"bb_img\" width=180 height=100 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PLAY WITH A FRIEND</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In co-op multiplayer mode, you can enjoy your adventure with a friend.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MORE AWAITS YOU</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect coins to purchase powerful items from merchants. Hidden diamonds and various achievements will keep you engaged even after you've completed the game.</p>",
